Last week, elite Hollywood producer, Steve Bing, “killed himself” and also 3 family members were ALL found “drowned” in a pool.  What’s the link between these two stories: they both had ties to the Clintons.  Steve Bing was extremely close to the Clintons and was a MAJOR funder of democrats.  He even paid for Bill Clinton’s trip to North Korea to “rescue” two American journalists.  However, he also had ties to Epstein.  How close was Bing to Bill’s island activities and how much did he REALLY know?!
.
Of the three family members found drowned in their pool, Bharat Patel had notable ties to the Clinton Foundation.  His LinkedIn account stated that he had volunteer experience in India as the Executive VP of the Ekal Vidyalaya, which partnered with the Clinton Foundation since 2001.  What did Patel know about this connection?  Was the Clinton Foundation funneling money through this “humanitarian” foundation?  Or was there something even MORE sinister going on?
.
